{
  "text": "In this analysis of secondary outcome measures from a randomized, placebo-controlled trial of GEXR in children with ASD and significant symptoms of ADHD [CITATION_1] , we tested whether GEXR would result in greater improvements in oppositional behavior, anxiety, repetitive behavior, and sleep disturbance than placebo.",
